{"tid":170381,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【有片】47歲素顏靚太李綺虹搭港鐵 八達通出事擾攘黃埔站","createTime":"2017-03-24T16:27:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-25T12:29:54.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7ab98934249a8474e7cfbfdd9323de98663f8486","tid":170381,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T16:27:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170324/large/1490366371_7358.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170324%2Flarge%2F1490366371_7358.jpg&h=fae30b05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李綺虹同外籍老公返咗香港，同以往差別唔算好大。（讀者提供圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n94年香港小姐季軍李綺虹，雖然嗰陣輸咗俾冠軍譚小環，但係冇影響佢喺娛樂圈嘅發展，當選冇耐已經被安排去拍電視劇，佢啲半鹹半淡廣東話再加埋儍大姐形象，唔單止吸引到一班師奶觀眾，仲為佢帶嚟唔少拍電影嘅機會。直至04年李綺虹同未婚夫Corey奉子成婚兼返加拿大定居，終於減少幕前演出，到咗08年回流返香港拍劇，最後喺2012年約滿離開無綫。<br />\n<br />\n今年已經47歲嘅李綺虹，日前就俾《蘋果》讀者彭小姐透過「爆相爆片」捕獲，彭小姐話當日喺黃埔港鐵站見到佢同老公：「嗰陣李綺虹同佢老公準備入閘，唔知係咪老公嘅八達通出現問題，同地鐵職員喺閘口擾攘一輪先入到閘，嗰陣李綺虹冇化妝，但係佢保養得好好，同當年拍劇個樣變化唔大。」<br />\n跟住李綺虹同老公行咗落月台，雖然佢已經離開娛樂圈幾年，不過對鏡頭嘅敏感度仲係好高，彭小姐話：「嗰陣李綺虹見到我影相，蹺晒手邊行邊好唔耐煩，好避忌咁左擰右擰，避開鏡頭，最初佢老公都冇出聲，但係見到老婆個樣唔多開心，都忍唔住叫我唔好影相。」跟住佢哋行咗去第二個幕門等車，車到咗就即刻上車同搵咗位坐低。<br />\n查實李綺虹返咗加拿大定居之後，間唔中都會返香港，噚日李樂詩仲喺ig貼咗張佢同李綺虹仲有童愛玲嘅合照，三個人keep得好好，計吓數佢個仔都已經有13歲，唔知李綺虹又有冇心郁郁返香港拍吓劇呢？  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170324/large/1490366232_fd1a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170324%2Flarge%2F1490366232_fd1a.jpg&h=1203150c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n見到鏡頭，有啲避忌。（讀者提供圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170325/56475952\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170325%2F56475952&d=Fs4PzESj5DMZecC7Kr%2FqWP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=7f124b64\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170325%2F56475952&h=c40249b7\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170325/56475952</a>"},{"pid":"255a34fed9e27d412f0e7a071864413da295b753","tid":170381,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T16:49:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67ed69cfdffefc1788681f368e26d7ed3e5daea5","tid":170381,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T16:54:03.000Z","msg":"阿爽啊~~"},{"pid":"808198307c73b59e9812e8ea1411e5bb70003589","tid":170381,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T17:43:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41c522db6cc7d511bfe4e550764517fef2b4fc95","tid":170381,"uid":77788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T17:54:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4378e80693f5f929c607bcd4d7bc77624c98a9f9","tid":170381,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T01:20:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3b110db6a4b1fbc0d287e0829fa0d4ea5599788","tid":170381,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T01:30:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>阿爽啊~~</blockquote><br />\n慕蓮～<br />\n其實我唔覺得靚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c2fdd0719e1b394207c2bce88f37fcec1ecdad1","tid":170381,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T02:16:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>彭小姐話：「嗰陣李綺虹見到我影相，蹺晒手邊行邊好唔耐煩，好避忌咁左擰右擰，避開鏡頭，最初佢老公都冇出聲，但係見到老婆個樣唔多開心，都忍唔住叫我唔好影相。」跟住佢哋行咗去第二個幕門等車，車到咗就即刻上車同搵咗位坐低。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁撚無恥嘅</blockquote><br />\n唔識問準人先影<br />\n好撚冇禮貌"},{"pid":"673fb4c50d1531bcd485eb0325c88324